==特征==
長{{convert|40|–|50|cm|in|2|abbr=in}}，但也有個體能夠達到{{convert|63|–|80|cm|in|1|abbr=in}}，雌蛇比雄蛇長<ref name="Mal03">Mallow D, Ludwig D, Nilson G (2003). ''True Vipers: Natural History and Toxinology of Old World Vipers''. Malabar, Florida: Krieger Publishing Company. {{ISBN|0-89464-877-2}}.</ref>。它肖似[[毒蝰|毒蝰]]、[[極北蝰|極北蝰]]，但體型要比二者小得多，是歐洲最小的蝰屬蛇類。<ref>Arnold EN, Burton JA (1978). ''A Field Guide to the Reptiles and Amphibians of Britain and Europe''. London: Collins. {{ISBN|0-00-219318-3}}. (''Vipera ursinii'', pp. 215–217 + Plate 39 + Map 121).</ref>

